metadata.name: Coffee of the Day
metadata.description:
"A coffee a day keeps the doctor away."

Photo from a visit to the 2nd location of East Pole Coffee Co., which opened in the Poncey-Highland neighborhood of Atlanta, GA in June 2022. 

Landing page: https://www.atlantacoffeeshops.com/east-pole-coffee-company-poncey-highland

Blog post: https://www.atlantacoffeeshops.com/blog/east-pole-coffee-co-is-now-open-in-poncey-highland
